1
00:00:41,120 --> 00:00:42,520
Why haven't you left yet?

2
00:00:42,760 --> 00:00:43,640
I won't leave.

3
00:00:44,280 --> 00:00:45,740
I want to stay by your side.

4
00:00:46,360 --> 00:00:48,160
I have nowhere to go anyway.

5
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:50,080
Rather than staying in the deep woods

6
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:52,280
and worrying about being caught every day,

7
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:53,880
it's better to stay down here

8
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:56,090
and live a carefree life for a few days.

9
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:10,680
Stop messing around.

10
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:11,760
Cultivation, cultivation.

11
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:13,080
All you know is cultivation.

12
00:01:13,080 --> 00:01:14,440
Every day you're either doing good deeds

13
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:15,370
or cultivating.

14
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:15,920
Hey.

15
00:01:16,240 --> 00:01:18,320
Do you have any joy in life at all?

16
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:19,800
Cultivating the Dao,

17
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:20,800
doing good deeds,

18
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:21,560
cultivating the mind,

19
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:22,840
and bringing peace to the world.

20
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:25,039
This is what we cultivators pursue.

21
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:27,820
How could there be no joy in it?

22
00:01:28,360 --> 00:01:29,200
Then...

23
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:30,860
What about having fun?

24
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:32,280
I am no longer a child.

25
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:33,850
I have no desire to play.

26
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:35,570
If you are bored,

27
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:38,020
just take a walk around the mountain.

28
00:01:39,039 --> 00:01:40,000
Stinky Daoist!

29
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:42,020
How dare you call me childish?

30
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,850
I'm telling you,

31
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:44,960
even if you beg me in the future,

32
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:46,160
I won't play with you.

33
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:06,100
My Silver Lotus Grass tastes better.

34
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:08,120
The way you humans eat

35
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:10,100
is much more cruel than us demons.

36
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:11,720
Not only do you kill them,

37
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:12,980
but you also boil them.

38
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:13,880
And

39
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,680
it doesn't taste good at all.

40
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:16,680
It's not as useful

41
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,520
as me absorbing

42
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,320
the moonlight essence at night.

43
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:22,280
Although you eat them raw without cooking,

44
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,360
the ultimate goal

45
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:27,090
is to sustain or elevate yourselves with other species' lives.

46
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:29,040
In this regard,

47
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:32,050
there is no difference between our two races.

48
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,200
You are clearly a Taoist,

49
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:35,920
not a monk.

50
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,000
Why are you so wordy?

51
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:40,640
Silver Lotus Grass,

52
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:42,240
are you going to eat it or not?

53
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,760
Such a good thing,

54
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,720
how could I not eat it?

55
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:56,400
I see you

56
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,720
practicing under the moonlight at night.

57
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:01,720
But it seems you don't practice any spells for fighting enemies.

58
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:04,180
I don't want to practice any killing spells.

59
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,330
We flower demons

60
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:07,680
are not born to fight with humans.

61
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,280
I just want

62
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,280
to be beautiful

63
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:11,320
and smell good

64
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:12,080
every day.

65
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:14,160
But the world is tough.

66
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:18,100
You still need the ability to protect yourself.

67
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,960
So you mean

68
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,200
I can attack humans?

69
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,290
That's not what I meant.

70
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:32,440
If I want to become lethal,

71
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:35,240
watering with blood is the fastest way.

72
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,160
No way.

73
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:40,000
You say no to everything.

74
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,520
What exactly do you want?

75
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:45,060
Learn some self-defense spells from me.

76
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,600
I don't want to learn.

77
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,240
It's difficult and tiring,

78
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:48,960
and boring.

79
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:50,079
I won't learn.

80
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,210
Let's go.

81
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,040
Cultivate.

82
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:10,780
Daoist Master,

83
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:13,240
I'm here to bother you again.

84
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:14,640
You...

85
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:15,480
A demon!

86
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:20,370
Cultivator, why

87
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,640
are you here?

88
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:21,899
I...

89
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:23,720
I...

90
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:26,000
My purpose here is no longer important.

91
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:26,520
Daoist,

92
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,900
is that a demon hiding behind you?

93
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:31,200
She is a demon.

94
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,680
But it has nothing to do with you.

95
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,480
Daoist Yuren,

96
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:36,370
why are you protecting a demon?

97
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,200
She has never harmed anyone.

98
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,930
You cannot treat her like this.

99
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,640
Demons are demons.

100
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,680
Humans are humans.

101
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,840
Demons and humans walk different paths.

102
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:44,680
Those not of our kind

103
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,760
are sure to have different hearts.

104
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:47,159
They must be eradicated.

105
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,120
I beg this cultivator

106
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,360
to let her go.

107
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:51,440
Daoist.

108
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:54,640
How many of our people have the demon and monster tribes killed?

109
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:56,600
My parents died at their hands.

110
00:04:57,159 --> 00:04:58,400
These evil demons

111
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,880
must be eliminated.

112
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:06,240
Little flower demon,

113
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,000
run away!

114
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:09,180
Don't even think about escaping.

115
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,320
Miss,

116
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,530
are you in some kind of trouble?

117
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,180
The world is ruthless.

118
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:36,600
Demonic cultivation is difficult.

119
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:38,400
Leave after your injuries heal.

120
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:48,720
No.

121
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,360
No.

122
00:05:58,840 --> 00:05:59,640
Taoist Master,

123
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:01,400
are there any demons around here?

124
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:02,130
Around here,

125
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:04,560
there are no harmful demons.

126
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:13,840
Little flower demon,

127
00:06:13,840 --> 00:06:14,400
run away!

128
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,280
No!

129
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,160
No!

130
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:28,240
No!

131
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:37,620
I see that at night,

132
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:39,680
you cultivate under the moonlight.

133
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:42,520
But it seems I haven't practiced any offensive spells.

134
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:45,000
If I want to become lethal,

135
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:47,720
watering with blood is the fastest way.

136
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:58,360
Such similar soul fluctuations.

137
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:00,760
Such a similar feeling.

138
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:05,880
But,

139
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,240
you are not him.

140
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,490
It's been thirty years.

141
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,920
You have never opened your eyes.

142
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:20,160
I originally thought

143
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:22,650
you might have already reincarnated.

144
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,280
But the moment I saw him,

145
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:31,970
I really thought you had come back to life.

146
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:35,640
Although you two are so similar,

147
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,400
I know

148
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,380
that person is not you.

149
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:43,659
Since that's the case,

150
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:47,080
then I will refine his soul.

151
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:49,410
It will definitely wake you up.

152
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:53,960
This is

153
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,600
the flower demon's memory.
